#Repost @lunarossachallenge
Luna Rossa Rewind Ep. 8 | Sealing the deal

On February 21st, 2021, Luna Rossa Prada Pirelli wins the last race of the PRADA Cup final against INEOS Team UK. A clean and impeccable race. With a score of 7-1, the team becomes the official Challenger in the Final Match of the 36th America's Cup presented by PRADA.
——
Il 21 febbraio 2021 Luna Rossa Prada Pirelli team vince l’ultima prova della finale di PRADA Cup contro il team inglese. Una regata pulita e condotta in maniera impeccabile. Con il punteggio di 7-1, il team diventa il Challenger ufficiale nel Match Finale della 36^ America’s Cup presented by PRADA.

#AmericasCup
#LunaRossaPradaPirelli #LunaRossa

node.text:
Umpiring in the 36th America's Cup is one tough job, you are making decisions that often come down to seconds or centimeters, and know half the audience will always disagree with you.

Would you do it?

node.title: The Toughest Job in the Cup ⚖️

node.text:
🇺🇸 @nyycamericanmagic were the first to launch a full-size test boat, and the first to sail and foil on an AC75. They were the first Challenger to set up in New Zealand and looked on track for a great regatta. However, it's PATRIOT's capsize and rebuild that has become their defining story of the 36th America's Cup.

👀 Follow the link in bio to watch the full story ☝
